  <name>Comicpress</name>
  <summary>Converts and compresses comics and manga for ereaders</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Comicpress takes DRM-free comic book files (CBR, CBZ, PDF) and compresses
      them to a fraction of their original size while improving how they look on
      e-ink ereaders. It applies image-processing operations such as contrast
      stretching, high-quality scaling, quantization, and dithering, all of
      which can be customized or disabled.
    </p>
  </description>

